title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>This release replaces the old <fr:code><![CDATA[\transclude*]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\transclude@]]></fr:code> commands with a more flexible transclusion configuration mechanism using the support for fluid binding introduced in <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-005O.xml"
addr="jms-005O"
